Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on wireless communication protocols for intelligent sensors. 
- cs.EM (Electromagnetics) is also likely as the paper discusses radio frequency wireless communication. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper evaluates the key features of different wireless technologies. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper discusses the integration and operation of a system that guarantees quality of communication and automation.
